type: flow_analysis
title: gem-research skill design - codebase analysis
key_insights[12]: Marketing AI Factory lives at /Desktop/dev/gem自動生成システム/marketing-ai-factory/,"SkillConfig dataclass in src/generator/models.py has: name, display_name, description, system_prompt, instructions, examples, knowledge_files, tools, temperature, constraints, guardrails, tags, metadata","Industry YAML configs follow pattern: keywords[], persona{}, tone{}, content_types[], platforms{}, hashtags{}, cta_templates[]","world-research has 6 layers (Academic->Curation->Blog->Ecosystem->SNS->Community), modes: quick/standard/deep/academic/survey/ecosystem","mega-research-plus has 8 sources with trust scoring algorithm: DA(0.25)+Freshness(0.2)+CrossValidation(0.3)+Citations(0.15)+SNS(0.1)",market_research.py uses Tavily/SerpAPI/Brave with async parallel execution and rate limiting via semaphores,"note_analyzer.py has NoteAnalyzer class with engagement calculation, search_by_keyword, batch_analyze","API routes have 3 research endpoints: /api/research/market, /api/research/note, /api/research/sns (all TODO stub)","GemExporter transforms SkillConfig into Gemini-compatible JSON with instructions, tools, safety_settings, knowledge","BaseExporter ABC pattern: get_platform(), get_template_name(), validate(), transform(), export()","Skills dir pattern: SKILL.md (main) + optional CLAUDE.md (summary) + optional scripts/ dir","gem-research must output JSON matching industry YAML structure: keywords, persona, tone, content_types, platforms, hashtags, cta_templates"
